name: The Magical Item #4 Jaru The Dogs Kingdom
description:
Getting out of Uyun tunnel allowed Dino to finally reach land. 
The intensity of the challenge knocked him out and he found himself laying unconscious on the shore. He was directly taken to Jaru, the Dogs Kingdom, to celebrate with King Kay. The ritual enabled Dino's soul to detach from his body. He connected with the dogs’ spirits and unlocked the Jaru fairy which will accompany and protect him during his adventures. Unlocking this portal will increase your Protection Attribute by 420 MPs.
